data.description: Charming, 2 story home on a corner lot. All bedrooms upstairs, including a cozy loft area. Open kitchen with breakfast nook and bay window. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. Ceramic tile downstairs, laminate flooring in living area, stairs and carpet upstairs. Nice oversized main bedroom with double vanity and separate garden tub and shower. The generous size backyard with the covered patio is perfect for those BBQ's. Convenient to 410,IH37, Brooks, Downtown, The Greenline Park , The Hardberger S.E Trailhead, and the Missions.
